This can be easily worked-around by avoiding Radium styles on the component's root element. Instead,  nest a `<div>` to hold the Radium styles.

For example, replace this component's root element style:

``` javascript
render() {
  return (
    <div style={{ display: 'flex' }}>
      <h1>{'Pure awesome'}</h1>
    </div>
  );
}
```

